G CLASSIFER SCREEN: Featuring 2 holes per square inch or 1/2 inch, this classifier is ideal to use at the beginning of the classification process when working with coarse materials; six inch depth allows for large amounts of material processing and can be stacked on top of a 5 gallon bucket</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">5 GALLON BUCKET: Gold rush sifting screen has been designed to stack on top of a 5 gallon bucket to create a vertical classification system, and is also compatible with all other ASR Outdoor steel mesh classifier screens</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HEAVY DUTY PLASTIC: Soil sifter is made of high quality and durable polypropylene plastic that will stand the test of time; rust and UV resistant and can be used in all kinds of weather; Rinse and air dry between uses</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FUNCTIONAL SIDE HANDLES: When classifying more coarse and heavier materials in the field, the built in side handles will make carrying, moving and sifting easier and less strenuous on hands, arms and back</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Size: 1/2 inch (2 holes per square inch); Top Diameter: 13.25 inches; Bottom Diameter: 10 inches; Depth: 6.5 inches; Color: Green</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1 style=\"color: black;\">ASR Outdoor 1/2\" Heavy Duty Stackable Bucket Classifier Sifting Screen with Side Handles</h1><h2 style=\"color: black;\">MSRP<span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"msrp-strike\" style=\"text-decoration: line-through 2px red;\">59.99</span></h2><h1><div class=\"col-md-6\" style=\"width: 360px; margin: 7.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400;\"><p>The newest addition to ASR Outdoor classifier screen product line up are these large, six inch deep stackable 5 gallon sifting screens with built in side handle, ideal for working with and sifting out gold rich pay dirt or other valuable sifted items from unwanted raw material. Importantly, these heavy duty plastic sifting screen is able to be stacked on top of a five gallon bucket, and are also compatible with all other sizes of ASR Outdoor stainless steel mesh classifiers.\n<br><b>Specifications To Note:</b>\n</p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Top Diameter: 13.25 inches</span></li><li>Bottom Diameter: 10 inches</li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Depth: 6.5 inches</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Mesh Size: 2 holes per square inch (1/2 inch)</span></li></ul><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">These heavy duty plastic gold rush sifting screens are ideal for working with coarse or more fine raw materials. Designed to be stacked on top of a five gallon bucket, use these plastic sifting screens or soil sifters to separate high value pay dirt from other unwanted organic material, like rocks, gravels, plant matter and aggregates.</span></div><div class=\"col-md-6\" style=\"width: 360px; margin: 7.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400;\"><br><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Two important design features to note: depth and built in handles. The depth of this plastic sifting screen is intentional and will allow you to move through much more raw material in comparison to a more shallow classifier screen. Lastly, when carrying and working with heavier and large amounts of material, you'll appreciate the two built in side handles, making the plastic sifting screen easier to maneuver.</span></div><div class=\"col-md-6\" style=\"width: 360px; margin: 7.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400;\"><br><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">ASR Outdoor heavy duty plastic sifting screen is made from tough and durable polypropylene plastic that will see you through many gold prospecting or rock hounding seasons to come. The high quality plastic material will never rust, making it a great classifier suitable for all types of weather. To maintain longevity, rinse and air dry between uses. The plastic classifier would also make a great gardening or foraging tool.</span>&nbsp;</div><div class=\"col-md-6\" style=\"width: 360px; margin: 7.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400;\"><br></div></h1>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p></div></div>",
